  • public class OdpCurrencyParam
extends OdpCompanyBasedAbstractParam
    Parameter class for ODP currency selection fields.

    This class extends OdpCompanyBasedAbstractParam to provide a dropdown/autocomplete list of currencies available in the ODP (Ordini Di Produzione) system. It retrieves currency data from the ODP service filtered by company and presents it as selectable items showing both currency code and description.

    This parameter is typically used in forms where users need to select a currency from the available ODP currencies (e.g., currency filters, currency selection fields).

    Author:
    RDS Software

    • Method Detail

      • getItemsList

        public com.rds_software.businesslogic.entities.ItemsList getItemsList(String filter,
                                                                      int from,
                                                                      int len)
                                                               throws Exception
        Retrieves the list of available currencies for display in dropdown or autocomplete fields.

        This method queries the ODP service to retrieve all available currencies and converts them into an ItemsList where each item contains the currency code and description. The items list is configured to render both code and description for better user experience.

        Note: The filter, from, and len parameters are inherited from the parent interface but are not currently utilized in this implementation. All currencies are returned without filtering or pagination.

        Specified by:
        getItemsList in class OdpServiceBasedAbstractParam
        Parameters:
        filter - the filter string to apply to the results (currently not used)
        from - the starting index for pagination (currently not used)
        len - the maximum number of items to return (currently not used)
        Returns:
        an ItemsList containing all available currencies with their codes and descriptions
        Throws:
        Exception - if an error occurs while retrieving currencies from the ODP service
